{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.60\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"d\">大衛與美索不達米亞並瑣巴的亞蘭爭戰時，約押回師，在鹽谷攻擊以東，殺了一萬二千人。那時，大衛作這金詩教誨人。交給聖詠團長，曲調用「為證的百合花」。</h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">求主解救</h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">（撒下8‧13）</h5>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>上帝啊，你丟棄了我們，破壞了我們；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">你曾發怒，求你使我們復興！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>你使地震動，崩裂；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">求你將裂口補好，因為地在搖動。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>你讓你的子民遇見艱難，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">使我們喝那令人東倒西歪的酒。</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>你把旌旗賜給敬畏你的人，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">可以躲避弓箭。（細拉）</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>求你應允我們，用右手施行拯救，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">好讓你所親愛的人得救。</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v6\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.6\" class=\"v6\">6</sup>上帝在他的聖所說：</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v6\">「我要歡樂；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v6\">要劃分<span class=\"pn\">示劍</span>，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v6\">丈量<span class=\"pn\">疏割谷</span>。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v7\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.7\" class=\"v7\">7</sup><span class=\"pn\">基列</span>是我的，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v7\"><span class=\"pn\">瑪拿西</span>是我的。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v7\"><span class=\"pn\">以法蓮</span>是護衛我頭的，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v7\"><span class=\"pn\">猶大</span>是我的權杖。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v8\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.8\" class=\"v8\">8</sup><span class=\"pn\">摩押</span>是我的沐浴盆，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v8\">我要向<span class=\"pn\">以東</span>扔鞋。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v8\"><span class=\"pn\">非利士</span>啊，你還能因我歡呼嗎？」</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v9\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.9\" class=\"v9\">9</sup>誰能領我進堅固城？</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v9\">誰能引我到<span class=\"pn\">以東</span>地？</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v10\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.10\" class=\"v10\">10</sup>上帝啊，你真的丟棄了我們嗎？</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v10\">上帝啊，你不和我們的軍隊同去嗎？</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v11\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.11\" class=\"v11\">11</sup>求你幫助我們攻擊敵人，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v11\">因為人的幫助是枉然的。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v12\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.12\" class=\"v12\">12</sup>我們倚靠上帝才得施展大能，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v12\">因為踐踏我們敵人的就是他。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}